@notice push a player to the array
@dev if the player already exists, it will not be added again
@param self Storage array contains an array of Player structures
@param player the player to add

@notice remove a player 
@dev finds the player to remove by his address, swaps it with the last player
     and then removes the player ;
     returns a boolean whether the element was found and deleted
@param self Storage array containing address type variables
@param player the player to remove

@notice check if a player exists in the array
@param self Storage array containing an array of Player structures
@param player the player whose existence we want to verify
